{"tid":31106,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"SMAP最後錄影唱《世界唯一的花》中居正廣不捨哭出聲","createTime":"2016-12-09T13:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T00:28:44.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e4876427c3954dff76e427278e42560d2fe86fa","tid":31106,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T13:00:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/524/d524777.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F524%2Fd524777.jpg&h=67e57fdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲SMAP解散倒數進入22天。<br />\n<br />\n日本傑尼斯天團SMAP將在31日解散，近日他們忙於為主持20年的冠名節目《SMAPxSMAP》收尾，5人一起合唱代表作《世界唯一的花》也將在26日播出。據悉，在錄影的時候，中居正廣因為不捨的情緒，20年來難得第三度在節目中落淚。<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/35/2016/01/26/3/3e0946873aa46d1ef00543fb88000bf6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F35%2F2016%2F01%2F26%2F3%2F3e0946873aa46d1ef00543fb88000bf6.jpg&h=70126dc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSMAP在最後一集節目中，邀來知名主持人塔摩利擔任嘉賓，並在8日完成了拍攝，長達5個小時的66歲李司棋偕女赴日露肉最終特集預定會在26日播出，內容包括經典畫面的回顧，以及SMAP 5人在1日所錄製的合唱畫面。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/AAljwrU.img?h=64&amp;w=80&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;u=t&amp;o=t&amp;l=f&amp;f=jpg&amp;x=488&amp;y=137\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FAAljwrU.img%3Fh%3D64%26w%3D80%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26u%3Dt%26o%3Dt%26l%3Df%26f%3Djpg%26x%3D488%26y%3D137&h=9cc6da38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSMAP 1日錄完5日的節目分量後，並緊接著錄製26日要播出的《世界唯一的花》演唱畫面。節目工作人員透露，在《世》曲音樂一停、攝影機停止拍攝的剎那，中居正廣突然就壓低帽子轉身，顫抖著肩膀哭出聲，他激動的情緒也感染到其他4名成員；木村拓哉甚至整整捂著臉30秒都沒動，為可能是最後一次的合體演唱而感到不捨。緩和情緒後，中居才頂著哭腫的雙眼，向工作人員們說「謝謝」，結束了錄影。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20160202/large/1454394043_e485.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20160202%2Flarge%2F1454394043_e485.jpg&h=654e9547&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據悉，中居正廣在節目中一共才哭過3次，第1次是森且行從團體離開時演唱《Best Friend》，第2次則是2013年成員5人初次一起旅行、並合唱《Best Friend》的時候，第3次就是此次解散前的最後演唱。"},{"pid":"e113c6b16dde7366e5106d56c2f1f65d25230833","tid":31106,"uid":22643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T13:20:39.000Z","msg":"中居真係一個好leader <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n木村而家做親Smap x smap都成日黑面 望天望地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個show係咁dead air<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f10087cfbe6fe949ed30e4806c94aca19e026b","tid":31106,"uid":8795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T14:15:08.000Z","msg":"66歲李司棋偕女赴日露肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa53a889a1c23cf290cbbe980ad840611548b3ab","tid":31106,"uid":43311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T14:20:25.000Z","msg":"我既SMAP <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都估到中居又會喊 <br />\n因為佢係最鐘意SMAP既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉<br />\nSMAP無左 連成宮寬貴都無埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e342331b73729fd35feacc5da29d305dffbbffcc","tid":31106,"uid":24739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:58:54.000Z","msg":"中居大哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af9998f8a9fa4d00b001a9bc8274643fc77cbfd1","tid":31106,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T16:16:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>66歲李司棋偕女赴日露肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做乜鳩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49d075be57dc06c183d63e5e76490812508206a","tid":31106,"uid":19466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T16:43:42.000Z","msg":"司棋姐做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"663aad180e22e65b66c642bbb09db0bb83e30c03","tid":31106,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T00:28:44.000Z","msg":"好鐘意睇中居<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}